depiction of <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Jewish</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">worshipers</ENAMEX> and use of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Kaddish</ENAMEX> were
