            <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Culturebox</ENAMEX> thinks the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Washington Post</ENAMEX> was faced with a genuine
dilemma but made exactly the wrong call. There is a tradition of <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">anti-Semitic</ENAMEX>
